<style>


/* CSS Variables */
[data-elementor-type="wp-page"]{
  --mac-menu-color: var(--e-global-color-primary);
  --mac-menu-bg: white
}

/* Underline menu */
.elementor-widget-jet-nav-menu .menu-item .jet-nav-link-text:after,
.jet-nav__sub .jet-nav-link-text:after{ 
  bottom: 0;
  content: "";
  display: block;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--mac-menu-color);
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
  width: 0;
}

.elementor-widget-jet-nav-menu .menu-item>a:hover>.jet-nav-link-text:after,
.elementor-widget-jet-nav-menu .current-menu-item > a > .jet-nav-link-text:after,
.jet-nav__sub .jet-nav-item-sub:hover .jet-nav-link-text:after,
.jet-nav__sub .current-menu-item .jet-nav-link-text:after{ 
  width: 100%; 
}

/* Sub menu Desktop */
@media (min-width:1025px) {
  .menu-item.jet-nav-hover>.jet-nav__sub.jet-nav-depth-0, 
  .menu-item.jet-nav-hover-out>.jet-nav__sub.jet-nav-depth-0 {
    top: calc(100% + 5px) !important;
  }

  .jet-nav__sub {
    width: max-content !important;
    padding: 5px 10px 5px 5px;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .menu-item > .jet-nav__sub.jet-nav-depth-0 {
    border: 1px solid var(--mac-menu-color);
    background: var(--mac-menu-bg);
  }

  .jet-nav__item.jet-nav-hover .jet-nav__sub::before,
  .jet-nav__item.jet-nav-hover .jet-nav__sub::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .jet-nav__item.jet-nav-hover .jet-nav__sub::before {
    top: -8px;
    border-left: 8px solid transparent;
    border-right: 8px solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 8px solid var(--mac-menu-color);
  }

  .jet-nav__item.jet-nav-hover .jet-nav__sub::after {
    top: -7px;
    border-left: 7px solid transparent;
    border-right: 7px solid transparent;
    border-bottom: 7px solid  var(--mac-menu-bg);;
  }
}   

/* Sub menu Mobile */
@media (max-width:1024px) {
  .menu-item .menu-item-link-top {
    width: 140px;
  }
  
  .jet-nav__sub {
    background-color: unset;
  }
  
  .jet-nav__sub .jet-nav-item-sub {
    width: fit-content;
  }

  .jet-nav__sub a:hover .jet-nav-link-text {
    color: var(--mac-menu-color);
  }

  .menu-item-link {
    justify-content: space-between !important;
  }
  
  .jet-nav-arrow svg {
    display: none;
  }
  
  .jet-nav-arrow:before,
  .jet-nav-arrow:after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    background-color: var(--mac-menu-color);
    transform-origin: 50% 50%;
    transition: all ease 0.5s;
  }

  .jet-nav-arrow:before {
    width: 1px;
    height: 15px;
    top: 2px;
    right: 27px;
  }
  
  .jet-nav-arrow:after {
    width: 15px;
    height: 1px;
    top: 8.5px;
    right: 20px;
  }
  
  .jet-nav-hover .jet-nav-arrow:before {
    transform: rotate(.25turn) !important;
  }
}


/*---booking-btn--- */
.mac_button_16 a{
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
}
.mac_button_16 a:before {
    transform: scaleY(1.2) scaleX(0.81);
    border: 1px solid var(--e-global-color-primary);
    z-index: -2;
}
.mac_button_16 a:before, .mac_button_16 a:after {
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
    transition: all ease 0.6s;
    background-color: transparent;
}

.mac_button_16 a:after, .mac_button_16 a:before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    }
    
.mac_button_16 a:after {
    transform: scale(1);
    z-index: -2;
    background-color: var(--e-global-color-primary);
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
}

.mac_button_16 a:hover::before {
    border-color: #fff;
    transform: scaleY(1) scaleX(1);

}
.mac_button_16 a:hover::after {
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transform: scaleY(0) scaleX(0);
    
}





</style>

<style>
    
/*--------------testimonial-----------------------*/

/* Desktop */
@media (min-width:768px) {
  .slick-track { padding: 60px 0; }
  .slick-center { z-index: 2; }

  /* Ẩn slide không active */
  .slick-slide:not(.slick-active) { opacity: 0; }

  /* Slide giữa */
  .slick-active.slick-center {
    transform: translateX(0) rotate(0);
    filter: none;
  }

  /* Slide bên phải của center */
  .slick-active.slick-center + .slick-active {
    transform: translateX(0) rotate(20deg);
    filter: blur(4px);
    opacity: .9;
  }

  /* Slide bên trái của center */
  .slick-active:has(+ .slick-active.slick-center) {
    transform: translateX(0) rotate(-20deg);
    filter: blur(4px);
    opacity: .9;
  }
}

/* Hiệu ứng chung */
.slick-slide {
  transition: transform .5s, filter .5s, opacity .5s;
}
.slick-slide:not(.slick-active) { opacity: 0; }

.testimonial-section .jet-slick-dots {
  gap: 10px;
}
.testimonial-section .jet-slick-dots li {
  padding: 8px;
  border: 1px solid transparent;
  border-radius: 50px;
  transform: scale(.9);
  transition: .3s ease all;
}
.testimonial-section .jet-slick-dots .slick-active,
.testimonial-section .jet-slick-dots li:hover {
  border: 1px solid var(--e-global-color-text);
  transform: scale(1);
}
.testimonial-section svg g { fill: #ffffff70 !important; }

.jet-testimonials__item-inner {
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  border-radius: 16px;
}

/* Tablet */
@media (max-width:1024px) and (min-width:767px) {
  .jet-testimonials__item-inner { margin: 0 -26px !important; display: flex; }
}

/* Mobile */
@media (max-width:767px) {
  .jet-testimonials__item-inner { margin: 0 -50px !important; display: flex; }
}



.gallery img {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    object-fit: cover;
}

</style>

settings.title: Where beauty, care, and relaxation come together.

settings.editor: Discover elegant nail designs, soothing spa treatments, and a welcoming space created to help you look and feel your absolute best. At Mac Nails & Spa, we believe every detail matters — from the quality of our products to the comfort of your experience. Whether you’re here for a quick polish, a full set of acrylics, or a calming spa treatment, our dedicated team is here to pamper you with care, creativity, and style.

At Mac Nails & Spa, we believe beauty is more than appearance — it’s about how you feel. Our mission is to provide a clean, relaxing, and friendly environment where every guest can enjoy high-quality nail care and spa services. With skilled technicians and attention to detail, we make sure you leave looking and feeling your very best.

From classic manicures and pedicures to custom nail art, acrylics, and rejuvenating spa treatments, we offer services designed to fit your lifestyle. Whether you want a quick refresh or a luxurious experience, our team is here to make it happen. Relax, unwind, and let us take care of the details.

At Mac Nails & Spa, your health and comfort always come first. We follow strict sanitation practices: every tool is thoroughly disinfected, every station is carefully cleaned between clients, and our staff is trained to maintain the highest hygiene standards. But beyond cleanliness, we care about your experience — from the moment you walk through our doors, you’ll be greeted with warmth, treated with respect, and welcomed into a space where you can truly relax and unwind.

settings.description_text: Every service is done with patience and precision so your nails look flawless and last longer.
Pick from hundreds of shades — from timeless nudes to bold colors, glitters, and seasonal trends.
Enjoy worry-free nails with our 7-day guarantee — we’ll fix chips or issues free of charge.

tabs.tab_title: 1. Do I need to book an appointment in advance?
tabs.tab_content: You’re always welcome to walk in, and we’ll do our best to accommodate you. However, booking in advance is highly recommended, especially during weekends or holidays, to make sure you get your preferred time slot and your favorite nail technician. Scheduling ahead also allows us to prepare for your service so you can enjoy a smooth, stress-free experience.

tabs.tab_title: 2. How do you keep tools and equipment clean?
tabs.tab_content: Cleanliness is one of our top priorities. All tools are thoroughly disinfected and sanitized after every single use using hospital-grade solutions. For pedicure services, we use disposable liners and replace them for every client to ensure the highest hygiene standards. Our staff is trained to follow strict sanitation protocols so you can enjoy your service with complete peace of mind.

tabs.tab_title: 3. How long does a manicure or pedicure usually last?
tabs.tab_content: The longevity of your manicure or pedicure depends on the type of service you choose and your daily routine. A regular polish manicure may last about 5–7 days, while a gel manicure can last up to two weeks, and acrylic or dip nails often last 2–3 weeks with proper care. Pedicures generally last longer than manicures since toenails grow more slowly, often staying fresh for 3–4 weeks.

tabs.tab_title: 4. What if my polish chips after my visit?
tabs.tab_content: We want you to love your nails even after you leave our salon, which is why we offer a 7-day guarantee. If your polish chips, fades, or doesn’t feel right within the first week, simply come back and we’ll fix it at no extra cost. Our goal is for you to feel confident with your nails, and we stand behind the quality of our work.
